      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Of course, let's refine your Monday schedule with a specific timeline and a quieter spot in Shibuya.\n\n**9:00 AM - 9:30 AM: Shibuya to Shibuya Station**\n- Take the JR Yamanote Line from Shibuya Station to Shibuya Station. It's a short 10-minute walk from your meeting spot.\n\n**10:00 AM - 11:00 AM: Shibuya Meeting**\n- Head to your meeting location in Shibuya. This gives you a bit of time to settle in and prepare.\n\n**11:00 AM - 11:30 AM: Shibuya to Hachiko Statue**\n- Walk to the Hachiko Statue, a quieter spot away from the main Shibuya Crossing. It's a great place to take a breather and enjoy the view.\n\n**11:30 AM - 12:00 PM: Hachiko Statue to Kappa Coffee**\n- Make your way to Kappa Coffee, a hidden gem tucked away in the Marunouchi Building. It's a peaceful spot perfect for work.\n\n**12:00 PM - 1:00 PM: Kappa Coffee Cafe Session**\n- Enjoy your lunch and work session at Kappa Coffee.",
